[I] Classical Mah Jongg game for four players

[T] Kajongg is the ancient Chinese board game for 4 players. Kajongg can be
[T] used in two different ways: Scoring a manual game where you play as always
[T] and use Kajongg for the computation of scores and for bookkeeping.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kajongg/

